{"tid":1512285,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［老香港好嘢］1922年，除咗《緊急情況規例條例》立法，仲發生咗乜嘢？","createTime":"2019-08-27T22:56:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T14:09:59.000Z","uid":310850,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"aa5aad29ce3f45a33e713f3dc133823db7a12aad","tid":1512285,"uid":310850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T22:56:40.000Z","msg":"噚日林鄭政府平地一聲雷，表明唔會「以暴制暴」（雖然popo其實已經好暴，睇睇Now新聞訪問北區醫院護士就知<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sNuDGV0eNRY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DsNuDGV0eNRY&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ6HX%2F1llhPerIglyOgZNoj0%3D&h=cfe42e35\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sNuDGV0eNRY</a>），而係用「法律手段」嚟「止暴制亂」，仲打算搬出一條可能勁過老解嘅古老法例嚟用。睇有線報道<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/186040714921338/posts/1194577560734310?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F186040714921338%2Fposts%2F1194577560734310%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ6HX%2F1llhPerIglyOgZNoj0%3D&h=bc720997\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/186040714921338/posts/1194577560734310?sfns=mo</a>，呢條《緊急情況規例條例》，基本上係打横嚟，政府做乜都得，睇落好得人驚下咁。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁嘅法例，大家印象最深係喺六七暴動用過，有啲歷史控即刻如數家珍<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/410201386052872/posts/616635035409505?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F410201386052872%2Fposts%2F616635035409505%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ6HX%2F1llhPerIglyOgZNoj0%3D&h=deb84ca7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/410201386052872/posts/616635035409505?sfns=mo</a>。不過，呢條例唔係喺六七年立嘅，而係喺1922年就有。嗰年發生咗乜樹，要殖民地政府生條咁嘅惡法？<br />\n<br />\n就係海員大罷工。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n維基都有講<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/香港海員大罷工\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%B5%B7%E5%93%A1%E5%A4%A7%E7%BD%B7%E5%B7%A5&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ6HX%2F1llhPerIglyOgZNoj0%3D&h=44ff2484\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/香港海員大罷工</a>，嗰次罷工，起因係英資船廠既海員要求加人工，英資夾埋港英極強硬，連海員工會招牌都叫英軍拆埋（真係拆㗎），結果人人返鄉下，個個唔上班。唔使用劍，唔使糾察線，更加唔使企車站門口，香港交通運輸就完全停頓，天星小輪都冇人揸，後嚟要政府派英軍揸。之後繼續仲多人罷，罷足56日，搞到要英國駐廣州總領使出嚟調停，最後加返人工、解封工會、撫恤鎮壓遇害家屬，港英政府先執得番掂個局，平息民憤。係維基睇返當年英軍還返工會招牌張張古董相，成街都係人，仲以為係早兩個禮拜影。啲老香港真係勁！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RypoHOu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRypoHOu.jpg&h=212a3af8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n講起嚟，呢條1922年嘅法例，出世咁耐用過兩次。六七暴動成地菠蘿都輸畀佢；但係面對1922海員大罷工，佢都收唔到科，最後都係要政治問題政治了。各位巴打絲打，跟住落嚟嘅日子，真係唔好睇少老香港嘅智慧呀～<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n識做就幫我大力推～～<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ce95d42fd37fa8c235acc0ba04f6513cee9ff39","tid":1512285,"uid":232295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T23:06:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09c47fa6442c6504189f00e9d577ec672408969a","tid":1512285,"uid":67098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa5aad29ce3f45a33e713f3dc133823db7a12aad","tid":1512285,"uid":310850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T22:56:40.000Z","msg":"噚日林鄭政府平地一聲雷，表明唔會「以暴制暴」（雖然popo其實已經好暴